      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Narrative / Story Library\n\nThis package models concrete authored story structure without drifting into literary-analysis abstraction.\n\nV1 classes:\n- `character`\n- `location`\n- `event`\n- `scene`\n- `artifact`\n\nDeferred:\n- `faction`\n- `motif`\n- `timeline-beat`\n- `relationship-note`",
