    {
      "id": "narrative-story-root-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Authoring Pressure",
      "position": {
        "x": 1040,
        "y": 220
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 240,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Authoring Pressure\n\nLikely typed relationships:\n- `Character` appears in `Scene`\n- `Event` occurs at `Location`\n- `Scene` contains `Event`\n- `Character` holds or seeks `Artifact`\n\nKeep the nodeset concrete and authored, not analytical.",
        "_classBinding": {
